snippet.title: Decisive Campaigns: Barbarossa Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Will you be in Moscow before Winter?

Barbarossa, the ultimate Eastern Front wargame is out!

Command a true operational structure. Can you balance and prioritise three different Theatres in order to achieve your objective?

Get the game here: http://bit.ly/1PBUsXG
